'''Nihonbashi Hie Shrine''' (日枝神社日本橋摂社) is a {{ill|Shrine|ja|神社}} located in {{ill|Tokyo|ja|東京都}} {{ill|Chūō Ward, Tokyo|ja|中央区 (東京都)|lt=Chūō|lt_ja=中央区}} {{ill|Nihonbashi Kayabacho|ja|日本橋茅場町}}. It is the external {{ill|Sessha|ja|摂末社|lt=Sessha|lt_ja=摂社}} of the {{ill|Hie Shrine|ja|日枝神社 (千代田区)|lt=Hie Shrine|lt_ja=日枝神社}} in {{ill|Chiyoda Ward|ja|千代田区}} {{ill|Nagatachō|ja|永田町}}.
It is also called '''Nihonbashi Hie Shrine'''.

==History==
